{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"One of the things that"},{"time":2000,"text":"defines a TEDster"},{"time":4000,"text":"is you've taken your passion,"},{"time":6000,"text":"and you've turned it into stewardship."},{"time":8000,"text":"You actually put action to the issues you care about."},{"time":11000,"text":"But what you're going to find eventually is"},{"time":13000,"text":"you may need to actually get elected officials"},{"time":15000,"text":"to help you out."},{"time":17000,"text":"So, how do you do that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":19000,"text":"One of the things I should probably tell you is,"},{"time":21000,"text":"I worked for the Discovery Channel early in my career,"},{"time":24000,"text":"and that sort of warped my framework."},{"time":26000,"text":"So, when you start to think about politicians,"},{"time":29000,"text":"you've got to realize these are strange creatures."},{"time":32000,"text":"Other than the fact that they can't tell directions,"},{"time":34000,"text":"and they have very strange breeding habits,"},{"time":37000,"text":"how do you actually work with these things? (Laughter)"},{"time":41000,"text":"What we need to understand is:"},{"time":43000,"text":"What drives the political creature?"},{"time":45000,"text":"And there are two things that are primary in a politician's heart:"},{"time":48000,"text":"One is reputation and influence."},{"time":50000,"text":"These are the primary tools by which"},{"time":52000,"text":"a politician can do his job."},{"time":54000,"text":"The second one -- unlike most animals,"},{"time":56000,"text":"which is survival of the species --"},{"time":58000,"text":"this is preservation of self."},{"time":60000,"text":"Now you may think it's money,"},{"time":62000,"text":"but that's actually sort of a proxy"},{"time":64000,"text":"to what I can do to preserve myself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67000,"text":"Now, the challenge with you moving your issue forward"},{"time":70000,"text":"is these animals are getting broadcast to all the time."},{"time":74000,"text":"So, what doesn't work, in terms of getting your issue to be important?"},{"time":77000,"text":"You can send them an email."},{"time":79000,"text":"Well, unfortunately, I've got so many"},{"time":81000,"text":"Viagra ads coming at me,"},{"time":83000,"text":"your email is lost."},{"time":85000,"text":"It doesn't matter, it's spam."},{"time":87000,"text":"How about you get on the phone?"},{"time":89000,"text":"Well, chances are I've got a droid who's picking up the phone,"},{"time":91000,"text":"\"Yes, they called, and they said they didn't like it.\""},{"time":93000,"text":"That doesn't move."},{"time":95000,"text":"Face to face would work,"},{"time":97000,"text":"but it's hard to set it up."},{"time":99000,"text":"It's hard to get the context and actually get the communication to work."},{"time":102000,"text":"Yes, contributions actually do make a difference"},{"time":105000,"text":"and they set a context for having a conversation,"},{"time":107000,"text":"but it takes some time to build up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109000,"text":"So what actually works?"},{"time":111000,"text":"And the answer is rather strange."},{"time":113000,"text":"It's a letter."},{"time":115000,"text":"We live in a digital world,"},{"time":117000,"text":"but we're fairly analog creatures."},{"time":119000,"text":"Letters actually work."},{"time":121000,"text":"Even the top dog himself"},{"time":123000,"text":"takes time every day to read 10 letters"},{"time":125000,"text":"that are picked out by staff."},{"time":127000,"text":"I can tell you that every official that I've ever worked with"},{"time":130000,"text":"will tell you about the letters they get"},{"time":132000,"text":"and what they mean."},{"time":134000,"text":"So, how are you going to write your letter?"},{"time":136000,"text":"First of all, you're going to pick up an analog device: a pen."},{"time":141000,"text":"I know these are tough, and you may have a hard time"},{"time":143000,"text":"getting your hand bent around it, (Laughter)"},{"time":145000,"text":"but this is actually critical."},{"time":147000,"text":"And it is critical that"},{"time":149000,"text":"you actually handwrite your letter."},{"time":151000,"text":"It is so novel to see this,"},{"time":153000,"text":"that somebody actually picked up an analog device"},{"time":155000,"text":"and has written to me."},{"time":157000,"text":"Second of all, I'm going to recommend that"},{"time":159000,"text":"you get into a proactive stance"},{"time":161000,"text":"and write to your elected officials at least once a month."},{"time":163000,"text":"Here's my promise to you:"},{"time":165000,"text":"If you are consistent and do this,"},{"time":167000,"text":"within three months the elected official will start calling you"},{"time":169000,"text":"when that issue comes up and say, \"What do you think?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":172000,"text":"Now, I'm going to give you"},{"time":174000,"text":"a four paragraph format to work with."},{"time":177000,"text":"Now, when you approach these animals,"},{"time":180000,"text":"you need to understand there's a dangerous end to them,"},{"time":183000,"text":"and you also need to approach them"},{"time":185000,"text":"with some level of respect and a little bit of wariness."},{"time":188000,"text":"So in paragraph number one,"},{"time":190000,"text":"what I'm going to tell you to do is very simply this:"},{"time":193000,"text":"You appreciate them."},{"time":195000,"text":"You may not appreciate the person, you may not appreciate anything else,"},{"time":197000,"text":"but maybe you appreciate the fact that they've got a tough gig."},{"time":199000,"text":"When animals are going to make a point, they make the point."},{"time":201000,"text":"They don't spend a lot of time dicking around."},{"time":203000,"text":"So, here you go. (Laughter)"},{"time":205000,"text":"Paragraph number two:"},{"time":207000,"text":"You may actually have to just get very blunt"},{"time":209000,"text":"and say what's really on your mind."},{"time":212000,"text":"When you do this,"},{"time":214000,"text":"don't attack people;"},{"time":216000,"text":"you attack tactics."},{"time":218000,"text":"Ad hominem attacks will get you nowhere."},{"time":220000,"text":"Paragraph number three:"},{"time":222000,"text":"When animals are attacked or cornered,"},{"time":224000,"text":"they will fight to the death,"},{"time":226000,"text":"so you have to give them an exit."},{"time":228000,"text":"Most of the time, if they have an exit strategy, they should take it."},{"time":231000,"text":"\"Obviously, you're intelligent."},{"time":233000,"text":"If you had the right information,"},{"time":235000,"text":"you would have done the right thing.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":237000,"text":"Lastly, you want to be the nurturing agent."},{"time":240000,"text":"You're the safe place to come in to."},{"time":243000,"text":"So, in paragraph number four,"},{"time":245000,"text":"you're going to tell people,"},{"time":247000,"text":"\"If no one is providing you with this information, let me help.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":251000,"text":"Animals do displays. They do two things:"},{"time":253000,"text":"They warn you or they try to attract you"},{"time":255000,"text":"and say, \"We need to mate.\""},{"time":259000,"text":"You're going to do that by the way you sign your letter."},{"time":261000,"text":"You do a number of things: you're a vice president,"},{"time":263000,"text":"you volunteer, you do something else."},{"time":265000,"text":"Why is is this important?"},{"time":267000,"text":"Because this establishes the two"},{"time":269000,"text":"primary criteria for the political creature:"},{"time":271000,"text":"that you have influence in a large sphere,"},{"time":274000,"text":"and that my preservation depends on you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277000,"text":"Here is one very quick hack,"},{"time":279000,"text":"especially for the feds in the audience."},{"time":281000,"text":"Here's how you mail your letter."},{"time":283000,"text":"First of all, you send the original to the district office."},{"time":286000,"text":"So, you send the copy to the main office."},{"time":289000,"text":"If they follow protocol, they'll pick up the phone and say, \"Hey, do you have the original?\""},{"time":292000,"text":"Then some droid in the back puts the name on a tickler"},{"time":294000,"text":"and says, \"Oh, this is an important letter.\""},{"time":297000,"text":"And you actually get into the folder"},{"time":299000,"text":"that the elected official actually has to read."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302000,"text":"So, what your letter means:"},{"time":304000,"text":"I've got to tell you, we are all in a party,"},{"time":307000,"text":"and political officials are the pinatas."},{"time":309000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":314000,"text":"We are harangued, lectured to,"},{"time":316000,"text":"sold, marketed,"},{"time":318000,"text":"but a letter is actually one of the few times"},{"time":320000,"text":"that we have honest communication."},{"time":322000,"text":"I got this letter when I was first elected,"},{"time":324000,"text":"and I still carry it to"},{"time":326000,"text":"every council meeting I go to."},{"time":328000,"text":"This is an opportunity at real dialogue,"},{"time":331000,"text":"and if you have stewardship"},{"time":333000,"text":"and want to communicate,"},{"time":335000,"text":"that dialogue is incredibly powerful."},{"time":337000,"text":"So when you do that, here's what I can promise:"},{"time":340000,"text":"You're going to be the 800 pound gorilla in the forest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":342000,"text":"Get writing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}